  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>sweet potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es] </span></strong>and <strong>white potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop the <strong>carrots</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and cut the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Peel 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>garlic clove<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642007484154-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642007484154-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642007484154-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642007484154-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642007484154-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray with <strong>baking paper </strong>then add the <strong>peeled garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong>, <strong>white</strong> <strong>potato</strong>, <strong>carrot</strong> and <strong>onion wedges</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, give everything a good mix up and put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 25 min or until everything is lightly charred and tender – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1642007499026-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1642007499026-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
