          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1642007499026-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate the <strong>remaining garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>king prawns</strong> and pat them dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Chop the <strong>drained prawns</strong> on a clean board until they are very finely minced (keep chopping until they become sticky!)</p><p>Combine the <strong>minced</strong> <strong>prawns</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>grated garlic </strong>and <strong>grated ginger</strong></p>",
