      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>trimmed ciabattas</strong> in half through the middle, then into 8 <span class=\"text-danger\">[16]</span> triangles</p><p>Spread the <strong>minced prawns </strong>onto the <strong>ciabatta triangles</strong></p><p>Press the <strong>sesame seeds </strong>onto the <strong>minced prawns</strong> – these are your <strong>prawn ciabattas</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
