    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to cover the base of the pan) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>prawn ciabattas</strong> and fry for 3-4 min on each side or until the prawns are cooked through and the toast is golden – these are your <strong>prawn toasts</strong></p><p>Tip: You may need to do this in batches, or use a second pan!</p>",
